<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>shén yǐ jīng lì tā 迦南264</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 shén yǐ jīng lì tā wèi jiù zhǔ wèi jī dū tā shì quán de de dà jūn wáng
 tiān xià rén jiān méi yǒu cì xià bié de míng wǒ men kě yǐ kào zhe dé jiù
 tā dài lái guān hū wàn mín de shì zhèn jīng zhōng wài zhèn jīng shì jiè
 tā shì wú zuì de gāo yáng bèi guà zài mù tóu shàng
 fán xìn kào tā de rén bì dé shì fàng bù zài bèi zuì è kǔn bǎng
 suǒ yǐ wǒ men dāng xiàng tā huān hū pāi zhǎng tā shì quán de de dà jūn wáng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>264</hymn_number>
</song>